      • onRegisterTable

        private akka.actor.typed.Behavior<Player.Protocol> onRegisterTable​(Player.RegisterTableMsg msg)
        Registers new Table to this Player. It is expected that a table position is already registered and it is replaced with the new ActorRef. When a excessive Table is about to be registered, IncorrectRegisterException is thrown.
        Parameters:
